</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>我们直接在元素上绑定自定义的指令<code v-pre>v-scroll-table=&quot;{cb: handleMore,infiniteScrollDisable: hasMore}&quot;</code>就行</p>
